              <span class="card-tag tag-remote" style="margin:0">Remote</span>
              <span class="card-tag tag-fulltime" style="margin:0">Full-time</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="job-actions">
          <span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);font-weight:500;">$120K–$160K/yr</span>
          <a href="jobs.html" class="btn-card">Apply →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="job-card fade-up">
        <div class="job-left">
          <div class="company-logo green">FV</div>
          <div class="job-info">
            <h4>Frontend Developer (React)</h4>
            <p class="company">Flutterwave</p>
            <div class="job-tags">
              <span class="card-tag tag-remote" style="margin:0">Remote</span>
              <span class="card-tag tag-fulltime" style="margin:0">Full-time</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="job-actions">
          <span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);font-weight:500;">$60K–$90K/yr</span>
          <a href="jobs.html" class="btn-card">Apply →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="job-card fade-up">
        <div class="job-left">
          <div class="company-logo orange">NB</div>
          <div class="job-info">
            <h4>UI/UX Designer</h4>
            <p class="company">Notion</p>
            <div class="job-tags">
              <span class="card-tag tag-remote" style="margin:0">Remote</span>
              <span class="card-tag tag-parttime" style="margin:0">Contract</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="job-actions">
          <span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);font-weight:500;">$80K–$110K/yr</span>
          <a href="jobs.html" class="btn-card">Apply →</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- LATEST NEWS -->
<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div>
        <p class="section-label">📰 Latest</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Industry News</h2>
      </div>
      <a href="news.html" class="view-all">More news →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <article class="news-card fade-up">
        <div class="news-img news-img-1">
          <span class="news-img-icon">🤖</span>
          <span class="news-category">AI Design</span>
        </div>
        <div class="news-body">
          <h3>Figma AI Launches Auto-Layout Assistant for Complex Design Systems</h3>
          <p>Figma's new AI features automate tedious design-system tasks and are already reshaping how product teams work.</p>
          <div class="news-meta">
            <span class="date">Jun 18, 2025</span>
            <a href="news.html" class="read-more">Read more →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="news-card fade-up">
        <div class="news-img news-img-2">
          <span class="news-img-icon">🌍</span>
          <span class="news-category">Africa Tech</span>
        </div>
        <div class="news-body">
          <h3>African Startup Ecosystem Raises $2.4B in Q1 2025 — A 40% YoY Surge</h3>
          <p>Fintech continues to lead, but edtech and health-tech are gaining fast ground across East and West Africa.</p>
          <div class="news-meta">
            <span class="date">Jun 12, 2025</span>
            <a href="news.html" class="read-more">Read more →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="news-card fade-up">
        <div class="news-img news-img-3">
          <span class="news-img-icon">⚡</span>
          <span class="news-category">Tools</span>
        </div>
        <div class="news-body">
          <h3>Vercel Introduces v0 AI: Generate Full-Stack Apps from Plain Text</h3>
          <p>Vercel's newest AI builder lets developers scaffold production-ready apps in minutes — no boilerplate required.</p>
          <div class="news-meta">
            <span class="date">Jun 8, 2025</span>
            <a href="news.html" class="read-more">Read more →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

